Summary: Introduction to implementing player jumping mechanics and monster squashing logic in the 3D game tutorial.

In this part, we will add the ability to jump and squash the monsters. In the next lesson, we will make the player die when a monster hits them on the ground. First, we have to change a few settings related to physics interactions. Enter the world of physics layers.
